  "instructions": [
    "1. Preheat oven to 425°F (220°C).",
    "2. In a large bowl, toss together olives, artichoke hearts, red bell pepper, spice blend, and a pinch of salt.",
    "3. Drizzle with olive oil and toss to coat.",
